tags.name: simple-concept-network
tags.description:
`simple-concept-network`
A small but effective little data visualizer for topics surrounding
a central concept, much like the ELMS:LN snowflake icon.

Attributes:

  * `visualization` {`string`} - Type of visualization

  * `disabled` {`boolean`} - disabled status

  * `coloredText` {`boolean`} - Apply color to text / icon instead of background.

  * `nodes` {`any[]`} - List of nodes to template stamp out

  * `accent-color` {`string`} - a selected accent-color: grey, red, pink, purple, etc.

  * `dark` {`boolean`} - make the default theme dark?

  * `colors` - make the default theme dark?
